::Kluster::

Kluster sighs, bombarded by comm messages and requests for 
help. "Proto, go to HotRod and help him out. Grimmler, go get the new 
Maximals."

The two Maximals stand up and exit the room. They recieve Iron 
Raptor's message. Grimmler sits down and Proto exits, heading for Hot 
Rod.
